36#include "gsskrb5_locl.h"
37
38OM_uint32 GSSAPI_CALLCONV _gsskrb5_duplicate_name (
39 OM_uint32 * minor_status,
40 gss_const_name_t src_name,
41 gss_name_t * dest_name
42 )
43{
44 krb5_const_principal src = (krb5_const_principal)src_name;
45 krb5_context context;
46 krb5_principal dest;
47 krb5_error_code kret;
48
49 GSSAPI_KRB5_INIT (&context);
50
51 kret = krb5_copy_principal (context, src, &dest);
52 if (kret) {
53 *minor_status = kret;
54 return GSS_S_FAILURE;
55 } else {
56 *dest_name = (gss_name_t)dest;
57 *minor_status = 0;
58 return GSS_S_COMPLETE;
59 }
60}
